quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,“Lemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wapamwambamwamba (ndikuliyeretsa ku zinthu zosayenera)
  87,2,“Amene adalenga (chilichonse) ndikuchikonza bwinobwino (mkalengedwe kolingana)
  87,3,“Amene adalamuliratu (chilichonse zochita zake) ndi kuchiongolera
  87,4,“Ndi Yemwenso akumeretsa msipu
  87,5,“Ndipo nausandutsa kukhala wouma ndi wodera
  87,6,“Tikulakatulira (chivumbulutso Chathu) ndipo siuyiwala
  87,7,“Kupatula chimene wafuna Allah (kuti uchiiwale); ndithu Iye amadziwa zoonekera ndi zimene zimabisika
  87,8,“Ndipo tikufewetsera (njira yochitira zinthu) zabwino
  87,9,“Choncho akumbutse (wanthu powalalikira) ngati kukumbutsa kuthandiza
  87,10,“(Palibe chikaiko ulalikiwo) aukumbukira (ndikuthandizidwa nawo) amene akuopa Allah
  87,11,"“Ndipo wamavuto ambiri, (wamakani ndi wokanira), adzitalikitsa ndi ulalikiwo"
  87,12,“Amene adzalowa ku moto waukulu (umene wakonzedwa kuti udzakhale malipiro ake)
  87,13,"“Ndipo sakafa m’menemo (ndikupumula kumazunzo), ndiponso sakakhala ndi moyo (wamtendere)"
  87,14,“Ndithu wapambana amene wadziyeretsa (ku machimo)
  87,15,"“Ndikukumbukira dzina la Mbuye wake (ndi mtima wake, ndi lirime lake) uku akumapemphera"
  87,16,“Koma inu mukukonda kwambiri moyo wa dziko lapansi
  87,17,“Pamene moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro ndiwabwino kwambiri ndiponso wamuyaya
  87,18,"“Ndithu izi (mukuuzidwa m’Qur’an) zilipo m’mabuku oyamba, akale"
  87,19,“Mabuku a Ibrahim ndi Mûsa